"},{"type":"text","text":"composed of multiple vertices."}],"type":"topic","title":"MLNMultiPoint","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipoint","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMultiPoint","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"title":"MLNAnnotation","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"objects to handle the display.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","role":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapSnapshotter/addAnnotations:":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter\/addAnnotations:","abstract":[{"text":"Adds an array of annotations to the snapshotter.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","title":"addAnnotations:","url":"\/docu